

y1 = a * x1 + b
y2 = c * x2 + d

b = y - a * x

===========================================

x1 = x2
y1 = y2

0 = a * x - c * x + b - d
0 = (a - c) * x + b - d
(a - c) * x = d - b

 => x = (d - b) / (a - c)

2 * y = (a + c) * x + b + d
2 * y = (a + c) * (d - b) / (a - c) + b + d

 => y = ((ad - ab + cd - bc) / (a - c) + b + d) / 2

